text: Fabiola Villalobos Morales (born 13 March 1998) is a Costa Rican international footballer who plays as a forward for the Costa Rica women's national football team. She appeared in two matches for Costa Rica at the 2018 CONCACAF Women's Championship. ==References== Category:1998 births Category:Living people Category:Costa Rican women's footballers Category:Costa Rica women's international footballers Category:Women's association football forwards
